entries.description:
Today’s speed build is a modern house in The Sims 4, using only the Base Game. I hope you enjoy, thanks for watching and don’t forget to like and subscribe ! :)

If you’re new to my channel, welcome ! I’m Pauline and I share Sims 4 speed builds as often as I can. I mostly build traditional family houses for your sims, using the Base Game and sometimes a few game packs too.

♡ Follow me on my social medias for more content ♡
